General_review: Master Chef is a restaurant located in Kuwait, serving a selection of Kuwaiti, Chicken, Seafood that delivers across Abdullah Al-Mubarak - West Jeleeb, Abdullah Al-Salem, Abu Ftaira, Abu Ftaira and Abu Halifa.
Their best selling dishes are Chicken Majboos, Mahashi with Meat, Meat Majboos and Fattoush Salad, although they have a variety of dishes and meals to choose from like Kuwaiti, Chicken, Seafood.
They have been reviewed 1548 times by talabat users, with a rating of 4.5.
